The evolutionary dynamics of u and v are modelled using the quantitative genetics approach31. The speed and direction of evolutionary change is proportional to the fitness gradient, evaluated at the current trait value. Prey and predator fitness are defined as the per capita net growth rates (i.e. Malthusian fitness) W
